config PROSPECTOR_APDS9960
    bool "Prospector APDS9960 ALS sensor"
    depends on DT_HAS_AVAGO_APDS9960_ENABLED
    depends on !APDS9960
    select GPIO
    select I2C
    select SENSOR
    help
      Enable Prospector's ALS-only APDS9960 driver. This driver binds to
      avago,apds9960 devicetree nodes and provides SENSOR_CHAN_LIGHT through
      Zephyr's sensor API without enabling proximity or the proximity LED.
